main event: A UFO was observed at Kadena AFB, Okinawa, on April 25, 1954, resembling a bluish white shining star.
interesting points: The object was seen making two turns and a circle over a duration of 5 seconds., The report indicates insufficient data for evaluation of the object., The object was described as having a silver color and a wing span approximately 50 ft., Eyewitnesses noted a zigzag motion before the object disappeared to the southeast., The observation was recorded by military personnel.
sighted object: one UFO described as bluish white and silver in color, shape like two saucers back to back
